name: Crimson Fleet Machinist
description: Tasked with maintaining the fearsome armored brigades of Mars while they are in transit, the machinists carry out their duty with utmost care.

name: Valerusi Striker
description: Many Kathari give a wide berth to the wild nature of the Strikers. Are they deadly? Most certainly. Effective? Sometimes.

name: Steward of the Garden
description: Some beat their swords into plowshares. She preferred a trowel.

name: Point Defense Turret
description: Few would dare mount a raid on one of the mighty ships of the Augencore. Those that do quickly meet their demise in a hail of return fire.

name: Orbital Strike
description: The clouds opened and for a moment they expected the warmth of the sun. Instead, they felt the fury of the Marcolian High Guard.

name: Singularity Steward
description: Every member of the Stewards would gladly give their life to prevent anyone getting close to discovering the Singularity. Thankfully, thats not a fight that many would be foolish enough to take.

name: Memento of the Fallen
description: The inscription on this battle-scarred knife simply reads, Live Forever - R. Cherry.

name: Black Market Fixer
description: You know what you guys look like? Like a couple of guys who just blew off somebody's head!

name: Mercenary Gunslinger
description: If youve got the money, Ive got the aim.

name: PS-8 Launcher
description: Direct Anti-Personnel projectile launcher. A solution as old as time, but an effective one none the less.

name: Lord Harf, Cartel Treasurer
description: No one is exactly sure why he calls himself a Lord, but so far, none have dared to ask.

name: Wong, Purveyor of Curiosities
description: I can offer you unlimited knowledge and worldly pleasures. Once a upon a time this stuff used to cost a lot more than credits

name: Security Officer
description: Trained to repel boarders & protect the secrets aboard Augencore vessels at all costs, Augencore Security are not to be taken lightly.

name: Kill Switch
description: Desperately outnumbered and beset upon from all sides, the valiant pilot had one last trick up their sleeve.

name: Hardlinked Pilot
description: Trained & bionically enhanced to be up to the task, these are the men & women who pilot the Augencores most devastating machines.

name: Rousing Signum [SE] - Artigraph
description: As mortars exploded overhead, Titus Gamma focused only on the Signum, feeling the anxiety and fear melt away.

description: Commander, it just came up on the star chart, it must have slipped in from an undesignated jump point - it looks like its an Echelon ship but it's not responding.

description: The Penshaw is an 18 gun battlecruiser intended to fly with a full complement of 190 souls. For Captain Kra and his crew of six, this was going to be quite the challenge.

name: Lunch Lady Bug
description:
The holders of the ten (10) Lunch Ladybug tokens were invited to one (1), ninety (90) minute lunch with Gary Vaynerchuk per "year" (i.e.). Each year was defined as the twelve month time period commencing on May 6, 2021, and May 6, 2022. In no event shall any experience (including this experience) occur after May 5, 2024.

In other words, there were two (2) total redemptions that occurred as follows:

One (1) redemptions must occur between May 6, 2021 and May 5, 2022
One (1) redemptions must occur between May 6, 2022 and May 5, 2023

This token has been redeemed for a ticket to VeeCon 2024. Please visit [VeeCon.co](https://veecon.co) to learn more about this year's event.

All access experiences were pre-scheduled in advance with 90 day notice via a VeeFriends representative.

This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain

name: Savannah
description: Savannah, a tiger-furred Fluf with an adventurous spirit, embraces life with unmatched enthusiasm. Her striking blue eyes are a captivating contrast to her wild fur, drawing others to her magnetic presence. Always ready for action, Savannah sports a pair of sunglasses to shield her eyes from the sun and maintain her cool image. She dons a high-visibility vest, a testament to her daring nature and love for embarking on thrilling escapades, no matter the danger. Savannah's casual demeanor is further emphasized by the cigarette casually hanging from her mouth. Her nose is adorned with a diamond stud, and her ears are decorated with gold studs, adding a touch of glamour to her otherwise rugged appearance. Her mouth is open to the right, expressing her free-spirited personality and her eagerness to share her latest adventures with anyone willing to listen. Savannah's chosen background is a Tiki setting, reflecting her love for exotic locales and the vibrant cultures they offer. The upbeat rhythm of "Ear Wobbler" fills the air, setting the perfect atmosphere for her energetic dance moves. As she bobs along to the music, Savannah's infectious energy radiates, inspiring those around her to join in the fun and embrace life's adventures with fearlessness and excitement.

name: Curio Card #17b (UASF)
description:
Starting May 9, 2017 Curio Cards were released weekly in sets of three. However when it came time for cards 17 to 19, an error with cards 18 and 19 made them unobtainable. The solution was to quickly release brand new versions of cards 17-19. This should have been the end, but by fate, the original card 17 was still purchasable but forgotten.

In March 2021, Curio Cards were rediscovered by NFT collectors. Being older than platforms like OpenSea, a [wrapper](https://wrap.curio.cards/) had to be created to make Curio Cards compatible. Just as the wrapper was being completed, daring ethereum archeologists discovered the secret of the forgotten card 17. Referred to now as the misprint card, this 17b card was found too late to include in the main wrapper, but is now available here.

Although entirely unintentional, 17b's story uncannily imitates the contents of its art: It tells the story of the UASF, a contentious proposal to create a duplicate version of Bitcoin in 2017. Maybe you can spot how the wrapped 17b artwork builds on this story?

Created by the same team as the official verified wrapper, this 17b-only wrapper has the same 1% artist royalty, going entirely to the original Curio Cards Artists. Join the [Curio Discord](https://discord.curio.cards/) and check out the [Curio Docs](https://docs.curio.cards/) to learn more.

name: Education
description: "Inspired by brains, ant colonies, and other complex systems, my art explores how global patterns arise via local relationships. The production of a drawing for me is actually not unlike the mining of a blockchain: an intricate process that can be laborious to perform perfectly, but with an intrinsic coherence that is self-evident after completion. Now with the creation of Curio Cards, the metaphorical mapping between cryptocurrencies and my art is meaningfully strengthened. Indeed now more than ever we are seeing the fusion of art with technology and science, reminding me of a favorite quotation by Goethe: '...science arose from poetry, and when times change the two can meet again on a higher level as friends....'. " - Daniel Friedman
